description: While a seemingly desperate Imran Khan has resorted to use toxic language against the united Opposition leaders and threatened a million strong assembly of supporters at D-Chowk on March 27, reports indicate that the die has already been cast with Pakistan Army deciding to remain neutral in the entire political play
